OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779930189
OL,3,CUber passengers will be able to record
OL,4,Cjourneys for 'peace of mind'
OL,6,FUber passengers with safety concerns
OL,7,Fwill be able to use the app to record
OL,8,Fthe audio of their journey from
OL,9,FThursday.
OL,11,FThe ride-hailing company said the
OL,12,Ffeature will give users "extra peace
OL,13,Fof mind".
OL,15,FPassengers will be able to activate
OL,16,Faudio recording through the app either
OL,17,Fbefore or during a trip, and then
OL,18,Fpress a button to start recording.
OL,20,FThe content will be encrypted and
OL,21,Fstored on the passenger's device.
OL,26,@tD@YOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
