FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779930189
OL,3,CUber passengers will be able to record
OL,4,Cjourneys for 'peace of mind'
OL,6,FIt will only be accessible to Uber,
OL,7,Fand only if it is uploaded through the
OL,8,Fapp as part of a safety report.
OL,10,FIt will be deleted after two weeks if
OL,11,Fa report is not made.
OL,13,FDrivers will be notified if audio
OL,14,Frecording is activated before a trip,
OL,15,Fand will have the option of cancelling
OL,16,Fthe booking without penalty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
