OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779930189
OL,3,CUber passengers will be able to record
OL,4,Cjourneys for 'peace of mind'
OL,6,FUber is also introducing a verified
OL,7,Fbadge which will show on the profile
OL,8,Fof a passenger who has had their
OL,9,Fpersonal details cross-checked with
OL,10,Fthird-party databases or has chosen to
OL,11,Fupload an official identity document
OL,12,Fand a selfie.
OL,14,FThis will be shown to drivers when the
OL,15,Fuser requests a ride from next week.
OL,17,FUber UK general manager Andrew Brem
OL,18,Fsaid: "We are always investing in new
OL,19,Fways to make journeys even safer.
OL,26,@zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
