OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779930189
OL,3,CUber passengers will be able to record
OL,4,Cjourneys for 'peace of mind'
OL,6,F"These new safety features provide
OL,7,Fboth riders and drivers with extra
OL,8,Fpeace of mind.
OL,10,F"Riders can record the audio of their
OL,11,Fjourneys securely, and drivers can
OL,12,Ffeel more confident about who is
OL,13,Fgetting in their car."
OL,15,FLocal transport minister Lilian
OL,16,FGreenwood said: "Everyone deserves to
OL,17,Ffeel safe when travelling, whether
OL,18,Fthey are a passenger or a driver.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@VO]xD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
