OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779930189
OL,3,CUber passengers will be able to record
OL,4,Cjourneys for 'peace of mind'
OL,6,F"I welcome Uber taking further steps
OL,7,Fto strengthen safety on its platform,
OL,8,Fgiving people greater confidence when
OL,9,Fusing private hire services, and
OL,10,Fshowing how technology can help make
OL,11,Feveryday journeys safer."
OL,13,FLucy Duckworth, of the Survivors
OL,14,FTrust, which represents rape and
OL,15,Fsexual abuse support services, said:
OL,16,F"We have to create a safety-first
OL,17,Fculture as a society, where people
OL,18,Frespect each other and unsafe
OL,19,Fbehaviour is challenged.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
