OL,3,CUber passengers will be able to record
OL,4,Cjourneys for 'peace of mind'
OL,6,F"These two new features are a positive
OL,7,Fstep toward giving drivers and riders
OL,8,Fmore confidence on their journey."
OL,10,FKola Olalekan, an Uber driver and
OL,11,Fbranch secretary for the GMB union,
OL,12,Fsaid: "I'm really glad to know that
OL,13,FUber riders can now be verified,
OL,14,Fsomething GMB have been requesting
OL,15,Ffrom Uber for a while.
OL,17,F"PHV (private hire vehicle) drivers
OL,18,Fpick-up passengers from a huge range
OL,19,Fof areas, at all hours.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@bO]tD@GOUyD@AOU
